w that, for equal-mass inner binaries,\nwhere the octupole terms vanish, the hexadecapole contributions can alone\ngenerate orbital flips and excursions to very large eccentricities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 May 2017 21:47:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Aug 2017 09:28:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-04"}
